title: Ask HN: Is there a platform to find experienced founders happy to mentor?
text: Does this exist? As a first time founder I'd love to be able to connect with experienced founders more easily than through networking events and I'm pretty sure that there must be quite a lot of people happy to share their expertise/ experience especially if they could see the focus topic straight away.

Ask HN: Does anyone know why VLC 3.0.18 is still not released?
text: I have noticed that apparently 3.0.18 was finalised around two weeks ago (https://code.videolan.org/videolan/vlc/-/tree/3.0.18). I've expected some delays for building, testing, and roll-out, but it seems that there's something that prevents releasing this update. Am I just imagining things or is there a critical showstopper that requires fixing?
